&lt;p&gt;An opportunity is available for a motivated Physiotherapist to build upon existing neuro skills, working within Community Stroke Rehabilitation; based in Bexhill Irvine unit providing early supported discharge and community stroke rehabilitation to patients across the Hastings and Rother CCG.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work within an interdisciplinary team including Physiotherapy, Occupational Therapy, Speech and Language Therapy, Nursing, Rehab Support Workers and Dietitian. The post holder will be supported to attend training within stroke and to develop not only their own practice but physiotherapy within the service.&lt;/p&gt;
